---
title: Chipotle-Glazed Chicken with Roast Veggie Toss & Corn Chip Crunch
description: Jazz up juicy chicken tenders by coating them in a lip-smacking mild chipotle sauce, along with our tried and true
All-American spice blend. Serve over a bed of hearty roasted veggies and add the finishing touches with a moreish
corn chip crumble for crunch, plus a dollop of sour cream for some tang.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
